      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field validation",
      "description": "Particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements of internal pump flow at 3 L/min, 3000 RPM compared to CFD velocity fields. RMS velocity error 4.2% of bulk mean velocity; recirculation zone extent matched within one impeller channel width."
    },
    {
