      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "Pump pressure-rise characteristic validation",
      "description": "Simulated head-flow curve compared to experimental pump curve across full operating range. Maximum deviation 6.1% at off-design condition (2 L/min, 4000 RPM); within acceptable tolerance for MRL 5 validation hierarchy."
    }
  ],
